function_args: "{\"project_name\":\"greet_app\",\"file_path\":\"main.py\",\"content\":\"import tkinter as tk\\nimport logging\\nimport os\\n\\n# Setup logging to file in the project directory\\nlog_file = os.path.join(os.path.dirname(__file__), 'app.log')\\nlogging.basicConfig(filename=log_file, level=logging.INFO,\\n                    format=\\\"%(asctime)s - %(message)s\\\")\\n\\n# Function called when Greet button is clicked\\ndef greet():\\n    name = entry.get()\\n    if name.strip():\\n        message = f\\\"Nice to meet you, {name}!\\\"\\n        label.config(text=message)\\n        logging.info(f\\\"Greeted user with name: {name}\\\")\\n    else:\\n        message = \\\"Please enter your name.\\\"\\n        label.config(text=message)\\n        logging.info(\\\"Greet button clicked without entering a name.\\\")\\n\\n# Create the main window\\nroot = tk.Tk()\\nroot.title(\\\"Greeter App\\\")\\n\\n# Input field for name\\nentry = tk.Entry(root, width=30)\\nentry.pack(padx=10, pady=10)\\n\\n# Greet button\\ngreet_button = tk.Button(root, text=\\\"Greet\\\", command=greet)\\ngreet_button.pack(padx=10, pady=5)\\n\\n# Label to display messages\\nlabel = tk.Label(root, text=\\\"\\\")\\nlabel.pack(padx=10, pady=10)\\n\\n# Start the GUI event loop\\nroot.mainloop()\\n\"}"
